         <abstract id="aspace_d0610f986f19945d121b0bcaa005f1ab">Correspondence, writings, printed material, and miscellanea relating to Samuel William Dudley's career as a professor of engineering at Yale University and a mechanical engineer with the Westinghouse Air Brake Company.</abstract>
